  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><math alttext=\"left parenthesis 9 x Superscript 4 Baseline plus 8 x cubed right parenthesis minus left parenthesis 7 x cubed plus 5 x squared right parenthesis minus left parenthesis 3 x squared plus x right parenthesis\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>8</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>7</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mn>5</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></mfenced><mo>-</mo><mfenced><mrow><mn>3</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>x</mi></mrow></mfenced></math></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The given expression can be written in the form <math alttext=\"9 x Superscript 4 plus x cubed plus a x squared minus x\"><mn>9</mn><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo>-</mo><mi>x</mi></math>, where <math alttext=\"a\"><mi>a</mi>\n</math> is a constant. What is the value of <math alttext=\"a\"><mi>a</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
